snippet.title: The Sims 2 - Celebration Stuff Official Trailer
snippet.description: Must-have stuff for your Sims' celebrations!  Whether a backyard barbecue, birthday blowout, or fancy wedding, your Sims can host the social event of the season. Get more info at www.TheSims2.com.
